<emphasis id="B9666F4D606CFFDFFF54D66A8003B801" bold="true" box="[151,268,1376,1399]" pageId="9" pageNumber="160">TABLE 1.</emphasis>
Comparison of taxonomic features among 
<taxonomicName id="4C12C8DC606CFFDFFD26D66A82A3B801" box="[741,940,1376,1399]" class="Demospongiae" family="Spirastrellidae" genus="Spirastrella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hadromerida" pageId="9" pageNumber="160" phylum="Porifera" rank="species" species="mollis">
<emphasis id="B9666F4D606CFFDFFD26D66A82A3B801" box="[741,940,1376,1399]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="160">Spirastrella mollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C12C8DC606CFFDFFC78D66A8538B801" box="[955,1079,1376,1399]" class="Demospongiae" family="Spirastrellidae" genus="Spirastrella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hadromerida" pageId="9" pageNumber="160" phylum="Porifera" rank="species" species="coccinea">
<emphasis id="B9666F4D606CFFDFFC78D66A8538B801" box="[955,1079,1376,1399]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="160">S. coccinea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C12C8DC606CFFDFFBADD66A85E2B801" box="[1134,1261,1376,1399]" class="Demospongiae" family="Spirastrellidae" genus="Spirastrella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hadromerida" pageId="9" pageNumber="160" phylum="Porifera" rank="species" species="hartmani">
<emphasis id="B9666F4D606CFFDFFBADD66A85E2B801" box="[1134,1261,1376,1399]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="160">S. hartmani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sheltered in the CNPGG.
</paragraph>
